  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN US ON DISCORD</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/d91a3a29a941390396da36b29fab9612.webp?t=1726226938\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/e409abbcc4601aef369b0fcff707e2ed.poster.avif?t=1726226938\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/e409abbcc4601aef369b0fcff707e2ed.webm?t=1726226938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/e409abbcc4601aef369b0fcff707e2ed.mp4?t=1726226938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Welcome to the Prospector: The First Contract - a prequel chapter where you take on your first contract as an Interstellar Prospector. Your main goal is to gather resources on a new planet. Build a living base, use supply routes for exploration, and automate your new home with robots. Once your preparations are complete, you will begin trading with distant colonies for exclusive rewards.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/707707ae8adf9f374447b35e06dd1254.webp?t=1726226938\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/40c1820bc31f6dc1d5c199090a8e7d63.poster.avif?t=1726226938\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/40c1820bc31f6dc1d5c199090a8e7d63.webm?t=1726226938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/40c1820bc31f6dc1d5c199090a8e7d63.mp4?t=1726226938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Scout out your surroundings by placing supply lines to provide life support in an oxygen-less environment.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/8b3a98b15f52d10ef8e6bb59534bc211.webp?t=1726226938\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/05932f273145da267181e2bbf611c278.poster.avif?t=1726226938\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/05932f273145da267181e2bbf611c278.webm?t=1726226938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/05932f273145da267181e2bbf611c278.mp4?t=1726226938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use collected resources to construct an outpost of your own design.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/4b9fefb1d5499f045e8fc9eb90a297a3.webp?t=1726226938\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/0406e8ba8aefd0d3b983a93a76d434eb.poster.avif?t=1726226938\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/0406e8ba8aefd0d3b983a93a76d434eb.webm?t=1726226938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/0406e8ba8aefd0d3b983a93a76d434eb.mp4?t=1726226938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Craft bots as helpers to automate the logistics of crafting and shipping goods.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/54f800e64106c5c5875d0b94c509ac03.webp?t=1726226938\" width=600 height=48 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/e78152dacfaf080774a2c56b56504881.poster.avif?t=1726226938\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/e78152dacfaf080774a2c56b56504881.webm?t=1726226938\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2730640/extras/e78152dacfaf080774a2c56b56504881.mp4?t=1726226938\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Scale your operation and ship more goods to make more credits which will unlock new blueprints for buildings and recipes for crafting.",
